Package com.company

Class TimeSlot

java.lang.Object
com.company.TimeSlot
public class TimeSlot
extends java.lang.Object
A TimeSlot object hold the information and methods of a time slot using the date (day, month, year) and hour. it also specifies whether the time slot is booked or not, and the Player it's booked to
